PN,42402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FThe 35-year-old had been driving the
OL,7,FFord Raptor which collided with a
OL,8,Fbarrier on the A69 close to Throckley.
OL,10,FMatthew Newton, 28, who was a
OL,11,Fpassenger in the car, died at the
OL,12,Fscene.
OL,14,FCCTV footage captured Neville driving
OL,15,Fdangerously as he left the city
OL,16,Fcentre, towards the A69.
OL,18,FShortly after 11.30pm, police received
OL,19,Fa report of a one-vehicle collision
OL,20,Fclose to Throckley.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FA heavy goods vehicle driver called
OL,7,Fthe police after coming across a the
OL,8,Fgrey Ford Raptor that had collided
OL,9,Fwith a barrier on the westbound
OL,10,Fcarriageway.
OL,12,FFollowing the collision, Neville fled
OL,13,Fthe area before police arrived. He was
OL,14,Farrested the following day.
OL,16,FNeville was later charged with
OL,17,Foffences including causing his
OL,18,Ffriend's death by dangerous driving
OL,19,Fand causing death whilst driving
OL,20,Fwithout insurance.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FDespite fleeing the scene,
OL,7,Finvestigators were able to prove
OL,8,FNeville was over the drink-drive limit
OL,9,Fat the time of the collision through
OL,10,FCCTV and financial enquiries.
OL,12,FThey discovered that Neville, of
OL,13,FCanonbie in Dumfriesshire, had been
OL,14,Fdrinking pints of beer, shots and
OL,15,Fspirits in a city centre bar with Mr
OL,16,FNewton for five hours before driving
OL,17,Fthem home, police said.
OL,19,FOn 23 January 2026, Neville pleaded
OL,20,Fguilty to all offences at Newcastle
OL,21,FCrown Court.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G4/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FHe was sentenced at the same court on
OL,7,FWednesday (25 March) to 11 years and
OL,8,F11 months and handed a seven-year
OL,9,Fdriving ban to start upon his release
OL,10,Ffrom prison.
OL,12,FRoss Neville drove to Newcastle city
OL,13,Fcentre with friend Matthew Newton,
OL,14,Fwhere he drank beer and spirits over a
OL,15,Ffive-hour period before getting back
OL,16,Fbehind the wheel
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FAt the hearing, a statement was read
OL,7,Fout from Mr Newton's mum Anna, who
OL,8,Fexplained the pain her family feels
OL,9,Fafter losing their "first born" child
OL,10,Fof three.
OL,12,FShe said: "The 28th November 2024 will
OL,13,Falways be the date that broke my heart
OL,14,Fand changed my life forever. My life
OL,15,Fas I knew it ended that day to be
OL,16,Freplaced with the mere existence I
OL,17,Flive with now.
OL,19,F"I never thought I would ever be in a
OL,20,Fposition to know what losing a child
OL,21,Ffelt like."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G6/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FShe added: "We have been robbed of
OL,7,FMatthew's future in the most
OL,8,Ftraumatic, horrific way, with so many
OL,9,Fthings stolen from us, seeing what he
OL,10,Fwould have become, seeing him get
OL,11,Fmarried, having children of his own
OL,12,Fand watching him proudly as he
OL,13,Ffulfilled his dreams.
OL,15,F"Instead, we now have to live with
OL,16,Fthis void in our lives and also watch
OL,17,Fhis brother, sister and grandparents
OL,18,Fheartbroken trying to adjust to a life
OL,19,Fwithout him."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42408
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FShe said: "Matthew was the most
OL,7,Fbeautiful person, had the absolute
OL,8,Fbest of friends, lived at home with
OL,9,Fus, would do anything for anyone,
OL,10,Fbuilt up a successful business and was
OL,11,Fsimply loved by everyone who knew him,
OL,12,Fhe had the brightest smile and lit up
OL,13,Fevery room he walked into.
OL,15,F"At 28 years old he should have had
OL,16,Fhis whole future ahead of him, now all
OL,17,FI'm left with is an empty chair."
OL,26,@nD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
