PN,42409
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,7,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,8,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,9,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,11,FSpeaking after the outcome, Sergeant
OL,12,FGreg Huntley of Northumbria Police's
OL,13,FSerious Collision Investigation Unit,
OL,14,Fsaid: "This was a shocking incident `
OL,15,Fwith Neville driving so dangerously
OL,16,Fand recklessly that he killed his
OL,17,Ffriend Matthew.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42410
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,F"Worse still, he has then went on to
OL,7,Ftell the HGV driver who came across
OL,8,Fthe crash that his friend was fine,
OL,9,Fbefore shamelessly fleeing the scene.
OL,11,F"It is clear to me that Neville was
OL,12,Fnot a good friend ` and he only had
OL,13,Fhimself in mind that evening as he
OL,14,Fleft Matthew with unsurvivable
OL,15,Finjuries in his car.
OL,17,F"Despite the challenges faced in the
OL,18,Fearly stages of the investigation, we
OL,19,Fwere able to trawl CCTV and financial
OL,20,Fdata to piece together Neville's
OL,21,Factions.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/12
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNE Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,425,420,120,260,000,100
PN,42411
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F424A1774537863
OL,3,CDrink driver who fled scene of crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed his friend jailed
OL,6,F"From this, we know that he consumed
OL,7,Falcohol to the excess in Newcastle
OL,8,Fcity centre before getting back in his
OL,9,Fpick-up truck to drive them home.
OL,11,F"He thought by running away he could
OL,12,Fhide how much he had drank ` but
OL,13,Fthanks to tireless work by officers we
OL,14,Fproved this in other ways."
OL,16,FSgt Huntley added: "As ever, our
OL,17,Fthoughts firmly remain with all of
OL,18,FMatthew's loved ones as they continue
OL,19,Fto navigate a life without him.
OL,26,@xD@TOU
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G11/12
